  "body": "### Problem\r\nSome edge case test scenarios require multiple transactions to be mined in a single block. Hardhat doesn't have any means of performing such tests.\r\n### Solution\r\nAdd a way of putting multiple transactions in a single block. A good solution would be exposing `miner_stop` and `miner_start` in the RPC API.",
